<style id="dashboard-styles-override">
.switchwrapper {
  margin: auto 0;
}
.toggle_radio{
    margin: auto;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 50px;
    position: relative;
    height: 19px;
    border: 1px solid var(--nr-dashboard-groupBorderColor);
    background: var(--nr-dashboard-widgetBgndColor);
}
.toggle_radio > * {
  float: left;
}
.toggle_radio input[type=radio]{
  display: none;
}
.toggle_4{
     width: 25%;
}
.toggle_3{
     width: 33%;
}
.toggle_2{
     width: 50%;
}
.toggle_radio label{
  display: block;
  height: 15px;
  margin: 0;
  line-height :15px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 1;
  text-align: center;
}
.toggle_radio label >p {
    background:transparent !important;
}
.toggle_option_slider{
  
  height: 15px;
  position: absolute;
  top: 2px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  transition: all .3s ease;
  z-index:0;
  left:2px;
  opacity:0.5;
  background: var(--nr-dashboard-widgetColor);
}
</style>
